{
  "stem": "1826.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we decided to-- he decided, and I decided to, to go away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then a group of people who originally came from a town Kremenets, Krzemieniec in Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they ran away from the-- they were afraid of the Soviets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were the richer people, and some of the richer people were taken away by the Soviets authorities.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they went to, to Lvov, to Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But now, they decided to go back to their-- to their town, to, to Kremenets.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I found-- my friend found out about it, and we decided to join them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They still had-- they had money, and they hired a truck with two German soldiers as guards.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were paid, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they went to-- they took us to Kremenets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were mostly Jewish people who were-- they were afraid because they were rich, relatively rich.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they-- they are afraid they were taking away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But now they thought-- they didn't realize all the situation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, they decided to go back to Kremenets, and I joined there, too, because I had my oldest brother lived in Kremenets.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came to Kremenets, and it was the evening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us on the same day, the Germans took away a few thousands of men, especially men, and took them away and were shot.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I've somehow managed to get to the place where my brother lived with his wife.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't have children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother had a little grocery store-- before, I mean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day a lady, a Russian lady, Russian-- her background was rather the Russian aristocracy, the Russian aristocracy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she used to be a customer of my brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she used to buy groceries there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
